comment.author: 68002240@N05
comment._content: Fw190G-3, WNr.160016 coded DN+FP, Later became EB-104 / Fe-125 / TE-12 This aircraft was operated by III./SKG10. It arrived at the Gruppe from Vicenza on 1 September 1943, and on 8 September was reported to have been with 9./SKG10. It was reported to have been destroyed by German personnel at Montecorvino on 9 September 1943, but the Allies reported it flyable after it was captured. See Lemb here: www.luftwaffe-experten.org/forums/index.php?showtopic=654...
